                        <interp inst="t18341124-name-194" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN CELER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a seaman on board the Claphyra. This blanket belongs to me—the prisoner had no authority to take it—I did not see him on board—I saw him standing on the quay as we hauled into the dock.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that he had found the jacket in the dock basin.)</p>
